Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Let's all make cards for those \Nwho celebrate their birthdays this month. {collection of words or drawings by several people on a single sheet of paper}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a nice present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja Neyo also has her birthday this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's today, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true? Show me, show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what everyone else wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday! Please get along with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to be a little more honest, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the heir to the Harako Conglomerate, Harako Tsutomu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you seem promising, \Nso I could make you my henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of Jabao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like no one was holding back. {unsure, maybe "everyone's writng is sloppy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, what you write? Write?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, maybe I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:28.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0E1D2C&\bord1\b0\3c&HA7B9C0&}Hey, Neyo. Happy birthday. \NPlease teach me to play kendama one of these days. \N\h                                                - Honmaru{ねえよ たんじょうび\Nおめでとう\Nこんど\Nけん玉おしえろよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Me write too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you sure, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Me learned the characters recently. To write my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:43.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fry180\c&H3A404A&\3c&HB3C4C0&}Taruru~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! These characters are backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo is reading the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is she really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.73,0:03:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?{g}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Exciting. Exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.20,0:04:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you throw away the card \Neveryone wrote for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See now, Iyona-san? I'm the agent of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Atomic Man Harako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.27,0:04:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's her deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's decisively unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! She's the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignored altogether...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The World Junior Agent of Justice, the Honorable Champion \Nof Atomic Man contest, I... got ignored altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo, why aren't you happy on your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll take it on myself to make Neyo happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You can do it, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dead end. She'll remain as the "Displeased Neyo", \Nno matter what you guys try. {maybe there wasn't any pun}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.91,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll make Neyo happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so caring. Good luck, Taru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, how do we go about doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Tickleflies. {こちょこ蝶}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This to make Neyo delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickleflies! Body-tickling butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it! Neyo happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nicely done, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, something feels wrong about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.19,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Neyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, did you do something to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll make you happy with this Babanger! {no clue what's original name, not in manga neither in wiki}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo! Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a little dizzy from this bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Me not give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will make Neyo happy at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, she's almost here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This - seeds of Congratonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You spread them on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you water them with this Congratuwatering Can. {fuck it, I gave up}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And in a blink of an eye, it bears the fruit of Congratonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:09:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Because tonus is another word for pumpkin. {literally, tounasu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she is, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratonus-san, counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Olive it to me! { I think this nasu in the end is pun with eggplant}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get radish, will you?{same}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get radish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday! Happy birthday! Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday! Happy birthday! Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are at it again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more times do I have to say it? {TLc, no clue what's ochakutte here}{9:53: I'm hearing "何度も人をちゃくって"\NNot entirely sure but this might be something:\Nhttps://jisho.org/word/%E7%9D%80%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B\NSpecifically the third definition.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! I swear to god...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, full steam ahead! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your next plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kendama! Conjure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Taru! What on earth do you need this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo! Neyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo! This for you! Birthday present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone {\i1}real{\i0} mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes beyond mad... {no clue what he means, maybe talking to neyo "don't get mad"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What would make Neyo happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Neyo want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey-hey, what should I do? Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.67,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,At times like this, it'd be nice to have some detective magic \Nthat can solve any riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I got this for such cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Detective Holmestick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Famous for solving the most perplexing of cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm a detective, alright. Itchy-itchy. {unsure what to make of to itch; to feel itchy; to feel creepy}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, Holmestick-san.  \NWhat present would make Neyo happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.41,0:12:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you gotta conduct a background check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You start by trailing her. \NCan you really not know even that? Itchy-itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disagreeable guy. {nanka iyamina}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's do tailing! \NNeyo, wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When tailing, you do it in a surreptitious way, you dimwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The best first step for that \Nwould be becoming transparent, itchy-itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! We're becoming invisible people with Magic-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Sword-Pen Magic-kun, eraser version \Ncan erase all sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Erase, erase, erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Me Invisibletective! {no clue if it's originally pun or not}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Better be quiet now, itchy-itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja really lives in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Big house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Yay! Elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.89,0:14:20.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H26201D&\3c&HA4A391&\b0}Apartment 506 \NZakenja Neyo \NZakenja Nezo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? She lives all alone with Nezo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Neyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our birthday today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So what of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom would probably congratulate us if she were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? A birthday? \NIt's just a sign that you're one step closer to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Brainless nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Try to investigate what's in her heart \Nwith Hearer. Itchy-itchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you! The old man's not coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not "old man," it's "daddy," Nezo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's have some fun, it's our birthday after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Very true! Now, Nezo-chan, you cheer up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.46,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo, happy birthday, alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our kind mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:52.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H302228&\3c&HA598A4&}Happy birthday \N\h            - Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this cake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... Why did you have to die? \NLeave us two behind? Why? Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru-chan, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.22,0:17:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If my mom died... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, stay strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be too much for me... \NBut Neyo has been living with this for a long time... {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to her, we definitely are \Nlike some spoiled brats! {g, not sure why "cant be helped"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:18:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been used to living without her mom for eternity while still attending elementary school. You're astounding, Neyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dad also barely ever shows up at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That also doesn't make \Nthe family environment one bit simpler. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In comparison, you could almost say I'm blessed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You assholes! When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! I can see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.36,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Magic wore off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Neyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They sneaked into my room without me noticing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw-aw-aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw-aw-aw-aw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that "aw-aw-aw?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ, what human trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to teach you this lesson again?! {lit: came again without learning the hard way}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo! Neyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing fine? \NMy, how big the two of you have grown! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nezo-chan, Neyo-chan, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're doing fine, \Nso I'm relieved now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is this heart TV? \NAre you kidding me?!{because "I'm not kidding around" doesnt fit in here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.49,0:20:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you're still alive, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People call it the afterlife. {/other world}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A pretty fun place, if I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lie, a lie! It's a dream, a dream, a dream, a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching over you two closely from here, \Nso don't worry. {considering what neyo and nezo have been up to lately, I'd doubt she'll be all happy about it}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.20,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're watching over us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.89,0:21:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the longer we talk, \Nthe harder it is for me. {no clue what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been watching over us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best birthday ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.06,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening! Delivery service here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy! {g}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The same shit as always has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it's getting my accustomed treatment this year as well. {established practice; custom}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.53,0:22:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray! Neyo happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! It's all thanks \Nto Spiritual TV-phone Hello-hello Itako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.78,0:22:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountains are nice, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Iyona-chan's bento is the best ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Bento, bento, bento!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.43,0:22:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Yamabiko Taro, an interesting magician. {やまびこ たろ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this guy a great deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.11,0:23:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun: \NFriends with Mountain Echo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.46,0:23:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I help Yamabiko, we can make the mountain clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.63,0:23:05.71,Sign,,0,0,0,,Episode 54\NFriends with Mountain Echo {やまびこ・友だち}
